OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1774271469
OL,3,CNew Archbishop of Canterbury arrives
OL,4,Cat cathedral following 140km pilgrimage
OL,6,FThe new Archbishop of Canterbury has
OL,7,Farrived at the city's cathedral
OL,8,Ffollowing a 140km pilgrimage ahead of
OL,9,Fher installation next week.
OL,11,FAs well as being the first woman to
OL,12,Fhold the role, Dame Sarah Mullally is
OL,13,Fthe first Archbishop of Canterbury in
OL,14,Fmodern history to undertake the
OL,15,Fpilgrimage.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
