PN,41702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1774271469
OL,3,CNew Archbishop of Canterbury arrives
OL,4,Cat cathedral following 140km pilgrimage
OL,6,FAlongside her husband Eamonn, she set
OL,7,Foff from St Paul's Cathedral in London
OL,8,Fon Tuesday afternoon, enjoying mild
OL,9,Fweather and bright sunshine for the
OL,10,Ffirst steps of her 87 mile journey to
OL,11,FCanterbury Cathedral.
OL,13,FThe final stretch of the journey saw
OL,14,Fthe pilgrims joined by David Monteith,
OL,15,FDean of Canterbury, and members of the
OL,16,FCathedral chapter, to walk from the
OL,17,Fvillage of Chartham to Canterbury,
OL,18,Farriving in time for Evensong on
OL,19,FSunday.( 22 March)
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
