PN,41703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1774271469
OL,3,CNew Archbishop of Canterbury arrives
OL,4,Cat cathedral following 140km pilgrimage
OL,6,FIn an interview just before she set
OL,7,Foff on the six-day walk, she said the
OL,8,Fpilgrimage will be an opportunity both
OL,9,Fto pray and to "encounter people in
OL,10,Fpart of my preparation" to take on her
OL,11,Fnew role in Kent.
OL,13,FShe had previously described it as
OL,14,F"deeply humbling to be following in
OL,15,Fthe footsteps of those who have walked
OL,16,Fthis ancient route".
OL,18,FBorn in Woking in Surrey in 1962, the
OL,19,FRt Revd and Rt Hon Dame Sarah Mullally
OL,20,FDBE is one of four children, with two
OL,21,Fsisters and one brother.
