PN,41704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1774271469
OL,3,CNew Archbishop of Canterbury arrives
OL,4,Cat cathedral following 140km pilgrimage
OL,6,FShe attended Winston Churchill
OL,7,FComprehensive School and Woking Sixth
OL,8,FForm College. She became a Christian
OL,9,Fat the age of 16.
OL,11,FBefore being ordained, she worked as a
OL,12,Fcancer nurse in the NHS, which she has
OL,13,Fdescribed as "an opportunity to
OL,14,Freflect the love of God".
OL,16,FDame Sarah Mullally will be formally
OL,17,Finstalled, or enthroned, at Canterbury
OL,18,FCathedral on Wednesday 25 March.
OL,26,@uD@NOUvD@XO]
